name: Turbinepunk Sky Pirate Ship
description:
Turbinepunk Pirate Ship equipped with a rocket turbine engine and special balloon-like apparatus covered with lace fabric. Turbinepunk is a retrofuturistic subgenre of science fiction similar to steampunk or cyberpunk that combines the aesthetics of the turbine-based technology from early jet engines till space race rocket engines with retro-futuristic technology and postmodern sensibilities.
6 sec round table 3d voxel render. 1500 x 1500 pixel.
